Caitlin Wachs https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caitlin_Wachs 0 Caitlin Elizabeth Wachs (pronounced wax; born March 15, 1989) is an American actress and production assistant who has acted in several films and TV series. She appeared alongside Ally Walker and Robert Davi in Profiler, and played the president's daughter, Rebecca Calloway, on the series Commander in Chief.Wachs was born in Eugene, Oregon. Her parents are Patrice Wachs, a graphic designer, and Allan Wachs, a producer of music videos.
